{"tid":1221711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【小整合】全面杯葛香港垃圾餐廳","createTime":"2019-06-14T09:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T12:06:55.000Z","uid":112901,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9df27a819e2e47f39f6afc09f7b516ec06362e2a","tid":1221711,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:26:03.000Z","msg":"眼見都有好多人抵制緊啲濕鳩親中餐廳，所以想整合吓相關資料，順便講少少建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1) 繼續報料，提供親中餐廳資料</span></strong></span><br />\n呢方面已經有巴打做緊，大家可以喺呢啲sheet度報料︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1IRdB2sEzIpKaMAsR9B_xCZmJtwNyR-8gzQbYtsWK__g/edit#gid=1529413945\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1IRdB2sEzIpKaMAsR9B_xCZmJtwNyR-8gzQbYtsWK__g%2Fedit%23gid%3D1529413945&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=c20cf0e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1IRdB2sEzIpKaMAsR9B_xCZmJtwNyR-8gzQbYtsWK__g/edit#gid=1529413945</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdfeHsyZ084eRKVKEC3CzfcnhBL-3JHqVpfB9FKokbVIS7z0Q/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdfeHsyZ084eRKVKEC3CzfcnhBL-3JHqVpfB9FKokbVIS7z0Q%2Fviewform&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=ed799979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdfeHsyZ084eRKVKEC3CzfcnhBL-3JHqVpfB9FKokbVIS7z0Q/viewform</a> <br />\n（名單見︰<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0/edit?usp=sharing）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing%EF%BC%89&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=ebcb27c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0/edit?usp=sharing）</a><br />\n<br />\n補充多句，長遠嚟睇最好可以整埋app/ 網站/ page等等，長期畀人隨時upload。抗爭唔係一時三刻嘅事，呢啲垃圾餐廳要抵制到世界末日為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">＊＊＊<br />\n原post︰<br />\n永久罷食/ 抵制餐廳名單（by 我愛老母）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1215706/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1215706/page/1</a><br />\n＊＊＊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外亦有都巴打整咗地圖，大家有時間可以將sheet嘅餐廳放落嚟︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=1UiDtBzI8MfZlLqDprhbxByutYaY9GdII&amp;ll=22.38336484842314%2C114.11736584999994&amp;z=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F0%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1UiDtBzI8MfZlLqDprhbxByutYaY9GdII%26ll%3D22.38336484842314%252C114.11736584999994%26z%3D11&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=a2d42b77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=1UiDtBzI8MfZlLqDprhbxByutYaY9GdII&amp;ll=22.38336484842314%2C114.11736584999994&amp;z=11</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">＊＊＊<br />\n原post︰<br />\n用Google map整緊愛國/愛港商業地圖，求報料（by 膠花）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1220413/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1220413/page/1</a><br />\n＊＊＊</span><br />\n<br />\nFacebook亦都有page畀人報料，大家有時間就share埋︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Boycott689/posts/2419659414980910?__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARChosFK47mN6DROJ96ViIh0H2poNLVvP6zEgPWG_PwGtMEySgOm22NpFoVDb5PWw3LqvPr8qILzXr1TYj7YPLOeHHGdHZ4eMnw5w8tQ0l2zrv0-29cvhGpdqoacziRmb06IXorfhLO9YK5DGnKNdhqDbBvfXx0Jsov7dUDk_2ujQLcfhG3_B_RqgjTCIfwtd0K9Yz3IsEPbIkoj7l7BL4-chEoUAk_FOfuzMi1jd68UNnu5BkvN48ljTl1dO3iaWFdr22xDeu6GC5-pjV9avpi0cb-OQ-m6gBqBFjuJ8QMT_3-OG-n0wB1vgejD17_avQDGuBfrJtCaU66KlnfAzbnbU0zZ&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBoycott689%2Fposts%2F2419659414980910%3F__xts__%255B0%255D%3D68.ARChosFK47mN6DROJ96ViIh0H2poNLVvP6zEgPWG_PwGtMEySgOm22NpFoVDb5PWw3LqvPr8qILzXr1TYj7YPLOeHHGdHZ4eMnw5w8tQ0l2zrv0-29cvhGpdqoacziRmb06IXorfhLO9YK5DGnKNdhqDbBvfXx0Jsov7dUDk_2ujQLcfhG3_B_RqgjTCIfwtd0K9Yz3IsEPbIkoj7l7BL4-chEoUAk_FOfuzMi1jd68UNnu5BkvN48ljTl1dO3iaWFdr22xDeu6GC5-pjV9avpi0cb-OQ-m6gBqBFjuJ8QMT_3-OG-n0wB1vgejD17_avQDGuBfrJtCaU66KlnfAzbnbU0zZ%26__tn__%3D-R&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=d7378ff9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Boycott689/posts/2419659414980910?__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARChosFK47mN6DROJ96ViIh0H2poNLVvP6zEgPWG_PwGtMEySgOm22NpFoVDb5PWw3LqvPr8qILzXr1TYj7YPLOeHHGdHZ4eMnw5w8tQ0l2zrv0-29cvhGpdqoacziRmb06IXorfhLO9YK5DGnKNdhqDbBvfXx0Jsov7dUDk_2ujQLcfhG3_B_RqgjTCIfwtd0K9Yz3IsEPbIkoj7l7BL4-chEoUAk_FOfuzMi1jd68UNnu5BkvN48ljTl1dO3iaWFdr22xDeu6GC5-pjV9avpi0cb-OQ-m6gBqBFjuJ8QMT_3-OG-n0wB1vgejD17_avQDGuBfrJtCaU66KlnfAzbnbU0zZ&amp;__tn__=-R</a><br />\n<br />\n**為咗方便記錄，大家報料最好提供埋完整資料︰餐廳名、餐廳地址、事件經過、證據（如有）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2) 將黑名單餐廳資料整合成一張圖</span></strong></span><br />\n因為sheet好難傳開去，去到咁上下可以將黑名單餐廳整合成一張圖，然後放上social media廣傳。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3) 寫吓你對呢啲餐廳嘅感受</span></span></strong><br />\n咁值得表揚嘅餐廳，唔係唔寫食評幫佢宣傳呀？小弟暫時諗到/搵到有呢啲平台︰<br />\n3.1 openrice (<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=0f6e8dfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong</a>)<br />\n3.2 google map<br />\n3.3 trip advisor (<a href=\"https://www.tripadvisor.com.hk/Restaurants-g294217-Hong_Kong.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tripadvisor.com.hk%2FRestaurants-g294217-Hong_Kong.html&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=9f0fc4ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tripadvisor.com.hk/Restaurants-g294217-Hong_Kong.html</a>)<br />\n3.4 ctrip 攜程 (<a href=\"https://you.ctrip.com/restaurant/hongkong38.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyou.ctrip.com%2Frestaurant%2Fhongkong38.html&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=42e15c81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://you.ctrip.com/restaurant/hongkong38.html</a>)<br />\n3.5 大眾點評 (<a href=\"http://www.dianping.com/hongkong/food/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dianping.com%2Fhongkong%2Ffood%2F&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=014730e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dianping.com/hongkong/food/</a>)<br />\n3.6 馬蜂窩 (<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/cy/10189/gonglve.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mafengwo.cn%2Fcy%2F10189%2Fgonglve.html&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=181d7cfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mafengwo.cn/cy/10189/gonglve.html</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4) 幫食環署監察餐廳環境</span></strong></span><br />\n如果大家喺呢啲餐廳見到或者懷疑見到小強，就記住同食環講喇～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">＊＊＊<br />\n食環署資料 (<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fcomments%2Fcontact_us.html&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=b5af5364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/contact_us.html</a>)︰<br />\n電話︰2868 0000 或 1823（24小時）<br />\n電郵︰enquiries@fehd.gov.hk<br />\n傳真︰2869 0169<br />\n地址︰香港金鐘道66號 金鐘道政府合署44樓 食物環境衞生署總部<br />\n＊＊＊</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5) 製作白名單</span></span></strong><br />\n真香港人絕對要幫返真香港人，尤其呢排又有舖頭出力畀物資，又有舖頭罷市。希望可以整返張白名單，記錄好人好事，等大家可以瘋狂幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n上面巴打個地圖已經收集咗一啲真香港人商店，但依家資料比較零碎，相信仲有好多良心小店，大家覺得需要嘅希望可以一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷市商店可以參考︰<br />\n【引渡惡法●三罷】6.12罷市！100毛CALL4VAN等逾440商戶參與（名單不斷更新）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190612/59697013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59697013&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=5f6667e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59697013&h=e2ccf0b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190612/59697013</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到呢啲，歡迎大家補充，香港人加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fc89fddc84abb20608eccbbb9d417374263c28","tid":1221711,"uid":112901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:36:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a47b295f89cf2e4ead7d0187709b39b95a20da9d","tid":1221711,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"83c4db589f3bf7a3d83ca75ed2e6100755ba5bc1","tid":1221711,"uid":248891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:10:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9175a8b0494c45653d7d1b15bbb82c011985cb3f","tid":1221711,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:14:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c337f2b7d16f52339f3bdeeb68414bbbe2f36c74","tid":1221711,"uid":14466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:14:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66792a6aba80b4b16ce0aae4ed9a3201d9d5706d","tid":1221711,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2ca22e3d7c761e83e36aaf42d29a3c07d29bdd44","tid":1221711,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2c26ee5ea627da388a54efa21fdd5ec4aae1bbd","tid":1221711,"uid":154263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:39:55.000Z","msg":"呢個一定要推"},{"pid":"bd18ced3d74d748c3438f6997c06d3d236dbd1fc","tid":1221711,"uid":2053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:41:30.000Z","msg":"關於大家可以點樣幫手舉報違規食肆，大家可以有以下幾個方法可以幫手，<br />\n<br />\n第一，去呢一度搜尋佢哋有冇持有有效嘅食物牌照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/licence-foodPremises-rest.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Flicensing%2Flicence-foodPremises-rest.html&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=cee33d1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/licence-foodPremises-rest.html</a><br />\n<br />\n通常市面上最常見嘅兩項牌照係小食牌照同埋普通食肆牌照，如果呢兩個項目都冇嘅，又或者係工廠區附近嘅，可能係工廠食堂牌照。<br />\n<br />\n如果初步查證發現沒有持有牌照記錄，可以同食物環境衞生署投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/tel_nos.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fcomments%2Ftel_nos.html&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=7f7cff58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/tel_nos.html</a><br />\n<br />\n第二，如果佢牌照上面冇問題，可以睇下佢哋衛生情況如何，例如街邊食肆好多時都有好多小動物，而且有啲鋪頭會打開廚房門，行去廁所途中有機會望得到入廚房嘅，睇吓佢哋地下有積水啊，廚師一路食煙一路煮嘢食呀，食物放咗喺地下等待處理之類。如果有嘅就影相留紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n另外最常見嘅食完野之後肚痛，最好有醫生紙證明。通常收到投訴食環署督察就會去鋪頭度檢視情況，好多時啲鋪頭都會中伏，會被食環署督察扣分，嚴重嘅會吊銷牌照。<br />\n<br />\n第三，根據過往嘅經驗，好多食肆會周圍擺放貨物，通道並唔符合消防條例，條例規定走火通道必須要最少闊1050mm ，如果發現有違規，可以影完相做紀錄之後去消防署投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/enquiry/g_enquiry/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfsd.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fenquiry%2Fg_enquiry%2F&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=2efb2c97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/enquiry/g_enquiry/</a><br />\n<br />\n上面講嘅所有方法全部都要實名登記投訴人，店舖係完全唔知邊一個人投訴。因為如果唔係實名登記，政府部門係唔會有任何動作。<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多好多招數舉報違規食肆，不過其他會比較麻煩，需要多啲相關知識。例如見到啲唔鹹唔淡廣東話嗰啲，可以去勞工處舉報懷疑請黑工。如果係散工嘅話基本上好多食肆老闆都唔會幫佢哋供強積金，同埋勞工保險。<br />\n<br />\n牌照方面好多食肆為咗慳錢，唔會做每年一次嘅消防年檢，通風系統年檢之類。不過就難啲有藉口去舉報佢。<br />\n<br />\n不過最緊要抵制名單真係要有證據先好，如果唔係好容易俾人利用去打擊其他鋪頭。"},{"pid":"2479244028a3552b60b70943451c763011a8de48","tid":1221711,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:41:39.000Z","msg":"M記就係最大中國餐廳, 又賣福喜肉<br />\n<br />\n但一樣日日咁多人排隊"},{"pid":"9d3424bc8986886d2810b347b25727e3da482610","tid":1221711,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd18ced3d74d748c3438f6997c06d3d236dbd1fc","tid":1221711,"uid":2053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:41:30.000Z","msg":"關於大家可以點樣幫手舉報違規食肆，大家可以有以下幾個方法可以幫手，<br />\n<br />\n第一，去呢一度搜尋佢哋有冇持有有效嘅食物牌照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/licence-foodPremises-rest.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Flicensing%2Flicence-foodPremises-rest.html&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=cee33d1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/licence-foodPremises-rest.html</a><br />\n<br />\n通常市面上最常見嘅兩項牌照係小食牌照同埋普通食肆牌照，如果呢兩個項目都冇嘅，又或者係工廠區附近嘅，可能係工廠食堂牌照。<br />\n<br />\n如果初步查證發現沒有持有牌照記錄，可以同食物環境衞生署投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/tel_nos.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fcomments%2Ftel_nos.html&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=7f7cff58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/tel_nos.html</a><br />\n<br />\n第二，如果佢牌照上面冇問題，可以睇下佢哋衛生情況如何，例如街邊食肆好多時都有好多小動物，而且有啲鋪頭會打開廚房門，行去廁所途中有機會望得到入廚房嘅，睇吓佢哋地下有積水啊，廚師一路食煙一路煮嘢食呀，食物放咗喺地下等待處理之類。如果有嘅就影相留紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n另外最常見嘅食完野之後肚痛，最好有醫生紙證明。通常收到投訴食環署督察就會去鋪頭度檢視情況，好多時啲鋪頭都會中伏，會被食環署督察扣分，嚴重嘅會吊銷牌照。<br />\n<br />\n第三，根據過往嘅經驗，好多食肆會周圍擺放貨物，通道並唔符合消防條例，條例規定走火通道必須要最少闊1050mm ，如果發現有違規，可以影完相做紀錄之後去消防署投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/enquiry/g_enquiry/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfsd.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fenquiry%2Fg_enquiry%2F&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=2efb2c97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/enquiry/g_enquiry/</a><br />\n<br />\n上面講嘅所有方法全部都要實名登記投訴人，店舖係完全唔知邊一個人投訴。因為如果唔係實名登記，政府部門係唔會有任何動作。<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多好多招數舉報違規食肆，不過其他會比較麻煩，需要多啲相關知識。例如見到啲唔鹹唔淡廣東話嗰啲，可以去勞工處舉報懷疑請黑工。如果係散工嘅話基本上好多食肆老闆都唔會幫佢哋供強積金，同埋勞工保險。<br />\n<br />\n牌照方面好多食肆為咗慳錢，唔會做每年一次嘅消防年檢，通風系統年檢之類。不過就難啲有藉口去舉報佢。<br />\n<br />\n不過最緊要抵制名單真係要有證據先好，如果唔係好容易俾人利用去打擊其他鋪頭。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望可以畀多啲人見到"},{"pid":"d76d6df88bed35ec950de953b01c9fbf5a7b1623","tid":1221711,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:44:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n不過最好有cap圖證明點解係blacklist"},{"pid":"e4647cebfd4ee445e8d328ef11ee0a97ddc9b11e","tid":1221711,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9459bd811226fe8f38f86aa1c178f3483a18511b","tid":1221711,"uid":222678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:55:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c7f7bd795015be1d138ead91550c1069da1cbbc","tid":1221711,"uid":148120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:59:36.000Z","msg":"如果整個app入面加個地圖，pin哂所有blacklist嘅餐廳，好似旅遊指南咁就最好！！！"},{"pid":"adafde0f2c552dd31cb83615c326f649d778b63c","tid":1221711,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2e3acd353ea2066aba1aee890e4e09b68d7ab37f","tid":1221711,"uid":112901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c7f7bd795015be1d138ead91550c1